{"tid":1358886,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"血濺元朗 5人仍留醫","createTime":"2019-07-24T04:21:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T04:31:10.000Z","uid":264914,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"dc01b5e9d1617a35a06cc8922493a3b37c3a6cd5","tid":1358886,"uid":264914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:21:03.000Z","msg":"元朗前日經歷黑暗一夜，白衣暴徒見人就打，釀成至少45人受傷流血事件。醫管局表示，傷者中目前仍有5人留醫，當中1人情況危殆、1人嚴重，另有3人穩定，其餘人已全部出院。傷者中，元朗流浮山叔父「飛天南」，送院急救後情況危殆，經手術後保住性命，據悉他經緊急通波仔後已蘇醒，仍須留醫心臟科深切治療部。<br />\n當日事件發生後，據悉單是屯門醫院外科接獲5名傷者，主要是骨折，頭頸有傷要縫針，其中一人被打爆面部顴骨，傷勢較嚴重。另一人除頭部被打傷需縫針外，更被打爆左眼，留有4厘米傷口，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>而且眼骨旁有外物刺入，可能是被木棍打時，有木屑進入傷口，要再由眼科醫生檢查如何進一步治理，暫時未知會否影響視力等。</strong></span></span>據知屯門醫院骨科也接收3名病人，主要是手腳等全身被打，有瘀傷。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>官商鄉警黑, 生仔無屎忽</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1f95441839a36d0d5f1b6d59001733470b8e1f9","tid":1358886,"uid":269681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:26:27.000Z","msg":"大家慢慢繼續用佢地黎拎光環<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />入元朗宣掦大愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24a82e0444464cc4f0734aed4eb9b40c0b3523be","tid":1358886,"uid":264914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T04:31:10.000Z","msg":"自推，口號創作，官商鄉警黑，下一句係咩好<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1358522/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1358522/page/1</a>"}]}